dmca.title: DMCA notice to Google, Inc.
dmca.body:
Image Received: 
Subject: Google Images Child Pornography Complaint
From: "Shantal Rands" 
On October 13, 2006 Google received notice of a site and two images in
our search results containing child pornography. We reported the site
and images to NCMEC and removed them from our search results.


(ImageID 8366)
